OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772817082
OL,3,CDefence secretary denies special
OL,4,Crelationship in trouble over response
OL,5,Cto Iran
OL,7,FBritain's Defence Secretary John
OL,8,FHealey has held talks with his Cypriot
OL,9,Fcounterpart over security fears raised
OL,10,Fby the drone attack on RAF Akrotiri,
OL,11,Fas ITV News' Shehab Khan reports
OL,13,FThe Defence Secretary John Healey has
OL,14,Fdenied the US is frustrated with the
OL,15,FUK's response to military action in
OL,16,FIran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772817082
OL,3,CDefence secretary denies special
OL,4,Crelationship in trouble over response
OL,5,Cto Iran
OL,7,FSpeaking from RAF Akrotiri in Cyprus,
OL,8,Fthe site of an Iranian drone attack
OL,9,Fearlier this week, Healey told ITV
OL,10,FNews: "We've agreed to the new request
OL,11,Ffor the Diego and Fairford bases. This
OL,12,Fis a really big contribution that's
OL,13,Fhugely valued by the US.
OL,15,F"There are things that we do as
OL,16,Fnations, the UK and the US, that no
OL,17,Fother nations do together. And this is
OL,18,Fa very deep decades-long relationship,
OL,19,Fparticularly on military and security
OL,20,Fmatters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772817082
OL,3,CDefence secretary denies special
OL,4,Crelationship in trouble over response
OL,5,Cto Iran
OL,7,F"It has survived the ups and downs of
OL,8,Fpolitics on both sides of the
OL,9,FAtlantic," he added.
OL,11,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer's
OL,12,Fgovernment has faced criticism from
OL,13,Fsome about a perceived slowness of
OL,14,Fresponse after it emerged the warship
OL,15,FHMS Dragon, which the government
OL,16,Fcommitted to sending to the region to
OL,17,Fbolster defence, will not reach Cyprus
OL,18,Ffor around two weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772817082
OL,3,CDefence secretary denies special
OL,4,Crelationship in trouble over response
OL,5,Cto Iran
OL,7,FAsked whether the UK was behind in its
OL,8,Fresponse when compared to European and
OL,9,FAmerican allies, Healey insisted: "No,
OL,10,Fwe're ahead."
OL,12,FHe continued: "We deployed
OL,13,Fstrengthened air defences in Qatar, in
OL,14,FCyprus, weeks ahead of the conflict
OL,15,Fbreaking out.
OL,17,F"We're ready to adapt the action that
OL,18,Fwe take in light of the changing
OL,19,Fcircumstances and threats we see from
OL,20,FIran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772817082
OL,3,CDefence secretary denies special
OL,4,Crelationship in trouble over response
OL,5,Cto Iran
OL,7,F"Everything that we have done has been
OL,8,Fcoordinated with other allies like the
OL,9,FUS, that helps, alongside the Brits,
OL,10,Fdefend this island, this base, our
OL,11,Fpersonnel and other allies in the
OL,12,Fregion.
OL,14,F"As the conflict evolves, as the
OL,15,Fcircumstances change, we'll adapt the
OL,16,Faction that we decide to take."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772817082
OL,3,CDefence secretary denies special
OL,4,Crelationship in trouble over response
OL,5,Cto Iran
OL,7,F"This is a very deep decades long
OL,8,Frelationship, particularly on military
OL,9,Fand security matters. And it has
OL,10,Fsurvived the ups and downs of politics
OL,11,Fon both sides of the Atlantic," said
OL,12,FHealey of the US-UK relationship.
OL,14,FTo date, the UK has only agreed to the
OL,15,Fuse of British bases and assets in a
OL,16,Fdefensive capacity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772817082
OL,3,CDefence secretary denies special
OL,4,Crelationship in trouble over response
OL,5,Cto Iran
OL,7,FQuestioned on whether this could
OL,8,Fchange to see the UK act in a more
OL,9,Foffensive role, Healey refused to rule
OL,10,Fout this possibility, saying: "Well,
OL,11,Fthe circumstances of conflict will
OL,12,Fchange, sometimes unpredictably.
OL,14,F"You've got to be ready to adjust the
OL,15,Faction. It's why today I'm sending in
OL,16,Ftwo anti-drone helicopters, which
OL,17,Fshould arrive overnight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772817082
OL,3,CDefence secretary denies special
OL,4,Crelationship in trouble over response
OL,5,Cto Iran
OL,7,F"In the coming days, we'll put a Type
OL,8,F45 Air Defence Destroyer into this
OL,9,Farea. It'll be part of our
OL,10,Fcoordination with the US and other
OL,11,Fallies and top defence planners
OL,12,Farriving in the island today to help
OL,13,Fcoordinate what other nations are now
OL,14,Fputting in alongside some of the air
OL,15,Fdefence and the strength and defences
OL,16,Fwe've had in Cyprus and Qatar for
OL,17,Fweeks ahead of the conflict."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
