FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772817082
OL,3,CDefence secretary denies special
OL,4,Crelationship in trouble over response
OL,5,Cto Iran
OL,7,FAs defensive measures are increased,
OL,8,Fthe UK has pledged to "rapidly" deploy
OL,9,Ffour additional Typhoon jets to Qatar
OL,10,Fto support regional defensive
OL,11,Foperations.
OL,13,FOvernight, a British Counter-Uncrewed
OL,14,FAerial Systems unit took down further
OL,15,Fdrones in Iraqi airspace that were
OL,16,Fheading towards Coalition forces.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772817082
OL,3,CDefence secretary denies special
OL,4,Crelationship in trouble over response
OL,5,Cto Iran
OL,7,FRAF F-35B and Typhoon fighter jets,
OL,8,Fsupported by Voyager air-to-air
OL,9,Frefuelling, flew further defensive
OL,10,Fsorties overnight, including over
OL,11,FQatar and Jordan.
OL,13,FThis is on top of an additional 400 UK
OL,14,Fpersonnel supporting air defensive
OL,15,Foperations across the UK's bases in
OL,16,FCyprus.
OL,18,FIn February 2025, the government
OL,19,Fcommitted to increasing defence
OL,20,Fspending to 2.5% of GDP by 2027.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772817082
OL,3,CDefence secretary denies special
OL,4,Crelationship in trouble over response
OL,5,Cto Iran
OL,7,FIt has since further committed to
OL,8,Fincreasing core defence spending to
OL,9,F3.5% of GDP by 2035, with some reports
OL,10,Fsuggesting Starmer is considering
OL,11,Faccelerating these targets to the end
OL,12,Fof this current parliament.
OL,14,FPushed on whether the UK is taking its
OL,15,Fdefence commitments seriously enough
OL,16,Fby spending appropriately, Healey
OL,17,Fdefended the government's record.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772817082
OL,3,CDefence secretary denies special
OL,4,Crelationship in trouble over response
OL,5,Cto Iran
OL,7,F"We're a government that's made a
OL,8,Frecord commitment to increasing
OL,9,Fdefence spending. The highest increase
OL,10,Fin spending since the end of the Cold
OL,11,FWar. An extra #5 billion this year
OL,12,Falone.
OL,14,F"The prime minister has said recently
OL,15,Fthat we need to spend more and faster.
OL,17,F"We will do what's necessary to defend
OL,18,FBritain, defend our allies, just as
OL,19,Fwe're doing in the middle of this
OL,20,Fconflict from this base here in Cyprus.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
